he group.  Also, when you are in a group your main purpose is to function to the best of your ability for that group.  Not to leave them hanging for a guildie or any other reason, because people do remember your actions and will relate you to your guild.  These are my thoughts on these subjects and the views expressed here may not be the views of management, heheh.  Talk to you in faerie land.<br>
<br>
